Name: Lavafish Stew Lv.1
Description: Recommend: Stormblade, Wind Knight, Heavy Guardian, Marksman, and Shield Knight.
Description$english: Recommend: Stormblade, Wind Knight, Heavy Guardian, Marksman, and Shield Knight.
Description2$english: A meat soup seasoned with high-quality spices, said to have an aroma that can stop passersby in their tracks while it simmers.

recipes.Name: Lavafish Stew
recipes.Des:
Crafting yields products Lv.1 and Lv.2 at rates of 80% and 20%, respectively.
Finely minced fish is simmered into a velvety broth, which is then used to slow-cook a rich and savory meat stew. Infused with premium spices, the stew exudes an irresistible aroma said to halt passers-by in their tracks.
